TEXT_HTML_WEBKIT_SAFE

public static final String TEXT_HTML_WEBKIT_SAFE
This Media (MIME) type is a fix to handle WebKit browsers which have a strange way of handling favorite mime types. Adding qs=2 specifies that the server would prefer serving HTML if possible. if we do not add that, WebKit will ask for ... XML! More info on: : http://jersey.576304.n2.nabble.com/ImplicitProduces-annotation-td5230574.html
